### Create a short URL
POST http://localhost:3000/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://google.com"
}

### Create another short URL
POST http://localhost:3000/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://github.com"
}

### Missing URL — should return 400
POST http://localhost:3000/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Redirect — replace abc123 with your actual code
GET http://localhost:3000/s2lzw4

### Bad code — should return 404
GET http://localhost:3000/xxxxxx